article:
This is a list of all space probes that have left Earth orbit (or were launched
with that intention but failed), organised by their planned destination. It
includes planetary probes, solar probes, and probes to asteroids and comets,
but excludes lunar probes (listed separately at List of lunar probes). Flybys
(such as gravity assists) that were incidental to the main purpose of the
mission are also included. Confirmed future probes are included, but missions
that are still at the concept stage, or which never progressed beyond the
concept stage, are not.
